text: Ethel is an unincorporated community in East Feliciana Parish, Louisiana, United States. The community is located along Louisiana Highway 19, north of Slaughter. Ethel has a post office with ZIP code 70730, which opened on September 15, 1884. ==Notable person== Jimmy Dotson, a blues singer, guitarist and drummer, was born in Ethel. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in East Feliciana Parish, Louisiana Category:Unincorporated communities in Louisiana
title: Ethel, Louisiana
